OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Fshowers will increase over Orkney from
OL,7,Fthe evening, these showers will clear
OL,8,Ftowards midnight. A bright evening for
OL,9,FShetland, then becoming cloudy from
OL,10,Flate evening but staying dry.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FThe day will be cloudy but
OL,13,Fmostly dry. Patchy rain may reach
OL,14,FOrkney for a time in the early
OL,15,Fafternoon and Shetland in the late
OL,16,Fafternoon. Fresh southeasterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
