OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloud
OL,6,Fand rain will clear north Sunday
OL,7,Fafternoon. Bright or sunny spells will
OL,8,Ffollow through the rest of the period
OL,9,Fwith showers at times. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
